  <brief_title>Study of Cingal™ for the Relief of Knee Osteoarthritis Compared to Triamcinolone Hexacetonide at 39 Weeks Follow up</brief_title>
  <acronym>Cingal17-02</acronym>
  <official_title>Extension Study to Cingal 16-02: Trial Extension to 39 Week Follow Up in the Randomized, Double-Blind, Active Comparator Controlled, Multi-Center Study of a Single Injection Cross-Linked Sodium Hyaluronate Combined With Triamcinolone Hexacetonide (Cingal®) to Provide Symptomatic Relief of Osteoarthritis of the Knee</official_title>
