  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this sub-study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety at 39 week follow up
      of a single injection of Cingal for relief of joint pain in subjects with OA of the knee who
      have not responded to conservative treatment (weight reduction, physical therapy, pain
      medications, etc.).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
